<article class='events'>
	{%- for event in events -%}
		{%- assign buildTime = 'now' | date: '%Y%m%d' -%}
		{%- assign eventDate = event.date | date: '%Y%m%d' -%}
		<article class='event | center box {% if eventDate > buildTime %}future{% endif -%}' id='{{ event.title | slugify }}'>
			{%- if event.image -%}
				<figure>
					<img src='{{ event.image }}' title='A photo of Tommi while hosting the workshop at {{ event.title }}' loading='lazy'
				</figure>
			{%- endif -%}
			<h2>{{ event.title }}</h2>
			<p>{{ event.location }} â€“ {{ event.date | date_to_string }}</p>
			<div class='flex'>
				{%- if event.url -%}
					<a class='yellow button' href='{{ event.url }}'>Event</a>
				{%- endif -%}
				{%- if event.notes -%}
					<a class='red button' href='{{ event.notes }}'>Notes</a>
				{%- endif -%}
			</div>
		</article>
	{%- endfor -%}
</article>

<p>If you are interested in hosting <cite>Knitting Our Internet</cite> at your event, you are welcome to <a href='/invite/'>invite Tommi</a> or <a href='/knit/'>go through the <cite>Weaver kit</cite> to host it yourself</a>!</p>
